Description: This package provides functions to calculate the ratio of iron oxides, hematite and goethite, in soil using the diffuse reflectance technique. The Kubelka-Munk theory, second derivative analysis, and spectral region amplitudes related to hematite and goethite content are used for quantification. Additionally, the package calculates soil color in the visible spectrum using Munsell and RGB color spaces, based on color theory.
